ngboilerplate(Angularjs framework) - project structure
grunt: task manager(like ant) -grunt file is a configuration of grunt build system 
bwoer-package manager - like maven

node.js - both grunt and bower runs on node.js



unit test:
For Unit tests I like JsTestDriver(http://code.google.com/p/js-test-driver/) + Jasmine (http://github.com/pivotal/jasmine) + JSTD Adapter(http://github.com/mhevery/jasmine-jstd-adapter)


