====how to compile=======
go to,app folder in cmd
C:\BCSWeb\BCSWeb\src\main\webapp\app

grunt watch

====how to install grunt and karma======
go to,app folder in cmd
C:\BCSWeb\BCSWeb\src\main\webapp\app
> npm install

Note: this will create node_modules folder. (inside grunt, karma, jasmine will be installed)





Note: when ever we do any js/html/css changes it will compile it into build folder

=====problem with npm install=====
this create a folder called -->node_modules
This folder has long paths..
after this only  ::: grunt watch (works for karma)
https://github.com/npm/npm/issues/3697

